{"tid":137934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美加州中國旅遊巴車禍 致1死26傷","createTime":"2017-02-28T08:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T11:21:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8834fe4c089efa2df87f5706d966e4cbc63657df","tid":137934,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/02/28/1501574_fd79a130a90fa6264650a0abe6a4a4e7_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F1501574_fd79a130a90fa6264650a0abe6a4a4e7_320.jpg&h=571b0fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於美國當地時間27日中午，加州聖伯納汀諾58號公路上，一輛載有中國遊客的旅遊巴行駛時突然闖入反向車道，與迎面兩車相撞，致其中一車司機死亡，另有26人受傷，其中7人重傷。<br />\n<br />\n該旅遊巴屬A&amp;F旅遊公司，事故原因正在調查。中國駐洛杉磯總領館正向受傷中國遊客提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1501574/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D+%E8%87%B41%E6%AD%BB26%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1501574%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D%2B%25E8%2587%25B41%25E6%25AD%25BB26%25E5%2582%25B7&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=85ddee8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1501574/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D+%E8%87%B41%E6%AD%BB26%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"49eeecace18a8b61d0cbe529880481aafd9471fe","tid":137934,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88aada47616e63f500d7479494246c60d3ab5a9d","tid":137934,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:11:15.000Z","msg